# 🚀 Skill Gap Scanner & ATS Resume Analyzer

> Upload your resume, paste a job description, and instantly discover missing skills, ATS compatibility, and actionable improvements.

🌐 **Live Demo:** https://skill-gap-scanner-ats.vercel.app/

---

## 📌 Overview

Skill Gap Scanner is an AI-powered web application that analyzes a candidate's resume against a job description and identifies:

- ✅ ATS Match Score
- ✅ Matching Skills
- ✅ Missing Skills
- ✅ Skill Gap Analysis
- ✅ Resume Improvement Suggestions
- ✅ Recruiter-Friendly Keyword Insights

The application helps job seekers optimize their resumes for Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS) and improve their chances of getting shortlisted.

---

## ✨ Features

### 📄 Resume Parsing
- Supports PDF resumes
- Supports DOCX resumes
- Automatic text extraction

### 🎯 ATS Score Calculation
- Calculates keyword overlap between resume and job description
- Generates a transparent ATS compatibility score
- Provides match quality indicators

### 🔍 Skill Gap Detection
- Detects skills present in the resume
- Extracts required skills from the job description
- Highlights missing competencies

### 💡 Smart Recommendations
- Generates actionable suggestions for every missing skill
- Helps users tailor resumes for specific roles

### ⚡ Fast & User-Friendly
- Modern responsive UI
- Instant analysis
- Simple drag-and-upload workflow

---

