```text
User Uploads Resume + Job Description
                │
                ▼
      Flask Backend API
                │
 ┌──────────────┼──────────────┐
 │              │              │
 ▼              ▼              ▼
Resume      Skill         ATS Score
Parser     Extraction     Calculation
 │              │              │
 └──────────────┼──────────────┘
                ▼
       Gap Analysis Engine
                ▼
         JSON Response
                ▼
         Frontend UI 
